
@startuml
title Dependency Direction

left to right direction
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho

package "Presentation Layer" as Presentation {
  component "UI / CLI / API" as UI
}

package "Business / Logic Layer" as Logic {
  component "Services / Use Cases" as Services
}

package "Domain" as Domain {
  component "Interfaces / Entities" as Interfaces
}

package "Infrastructure Layer" as Infrastructure {
  component "Database / File System\nExternal Services" as Infra
}

UI --> Services
Services --> Interfaces
Infra --> Interfaces
@enduml

– diagram
Presentation → Application → Domain
Presentation → Domain
Infrastructure → Domain

Domain
├── Project
├── Image
└── IProjectRepository

Infrastructure
└── ProjectRepository : IProjectRepository
